{
  "stem": "3150.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's on-- I think that's in the Temple Torah, right-- where my granddaughter went.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, it was not at my temple.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's in Dix Hills.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we had plenty-- plenty of problems, you know, it being-- being such a close quarters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody, you know, it's-- but somehow we survived.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, there's no question about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, everybody gets on each other's nerves.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's only one problem.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You couldn't leave.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] There was no place to go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But the normal, natural problems, you know, of every day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Somewhat.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think we probably came closer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we-- everybody thought, you know, we don't have the guy that's going to take care of us.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody looks up to my father.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So when he died, that probably made us closer, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "To-- everybody started worrying about more than before.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before it was well, he's going to take care of the-- you know, the image.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even though it was really out of his hands to do anything anymore, well, you know, you see.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But somehow you feel in your head, he's-- he's going to-- he's going to go you know, bring bread.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He's going to go-- he's going to-- if he's-- if guy throws us out, you know, he'll dig up another guy who's going to save you.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But after that, it was-- it was really scary.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because we know if this guy says-- comes down one and says, leave, where are you going to go?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we knew the guy that-- that kept giving us the food.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He'd do anything for you.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he cannot really take you in there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we knew that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because-- because they were really watching the Czechs, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
